page.title: 04CORNISH HEDGEROW - BOTANY
page.content: Two stretches of hedgerow running at right angles to each other, each 30 metres long, were studied in July.the following plants were identified:- {Foxglove Dandelion {Tufted Vetch Catsear {Yorkshire Fog Elm {Red Campion Bindweed {Meadow Foxtail Hedge Bindweed {Blackthorn Common Vetch {Lymegrass Common Field {Meadow Thistle Speedwell {Hawthorn Pineapple Mayweed {Bramble Groundsel {Nettle Common Ragwort {Common Bent Grass Goosegrass {Gorse Elderberry {Hogweed Cow Parsley {Cranesbill Tall Fescue {Creeping Thistle Hart's Tongue {Timothy Prickly Sow Thistle {Ivy Water Bent Grass
